{"tid":1985311,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"如郵寄申請行車證，過期行車費用點交架？","createTime":"2020-04-23T05:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T01:59:45.000Z","uid":253413,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f0526dedb3c15ab934edf850699873d00fbdb0ce","tid":1985311,"uid":253413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:23:33.000Z","msg":"我行車證17/4/2020到期<br />\n細車唔過1500cc一年牌費$3929（寫支票）<br />\n如果我而家先申請行車證，預佢10日先出到證<br />\n咁呢段期間要畀$3929x0.33%x20日$260左右<br />\n咁我係要點交呀？<br />\n寫埋落3929個張支票定另寫一張？<br />\n定等佢出左新證畀我先畀張繳費單我？"},{"pid":"ab529fdc05cfa4858950b663b927fb4b797e5a63","tid":1985311,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁on9明知而家咁嘅環境都遲續"},{"pid":"b03976fd0a10f802056eb385ebfa7f82321f0340","tid":1985311,"uid":253413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab529fdc05cfa4858950b663b927fb4b797e5a63","tid":1985311,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁on9明知而家咁嘅環境都遲續"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ac389bae3e469d5c342d44f373210271b86306","tid":1985311,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b03976fd0a10f802056eb385ebfa7f82321f0340","tid":1985311,"uid":253413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab529fdc05cfa4858950b663b927fb4b797e5a63","tid":1985311,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T05:49:30.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁on9明知而家咁嘅環境都遲續"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T06:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal